From: hmaarrfk <mark.harfouche@conda-forge.org>
Date: 2026-05-10
Subject: third_party: only pull test-only vendored deps when tests are on

Upstream unconditionally `add_subdirectory()`s third_party/googletest and
third_party/yaml-cpp even though both are only used by the validation
test apps under validation/umd-test/, which is itself gated by
ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD.  This forces downstream packagers to either
vendor those sources (against conda-forge policy) or carry patches like
this one.

* googletest is pure test scaffolding — guard on ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD.
* yaml-cpp is only #included from validation/umd-test/*.cpp — guard on
  ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD too, and switch from add_subdirectory() to
  find_package() so downstream packagers can supply yaml-cpp via the
  conda-forge / system package.

The library output of this driver (libze_intel_npu.so) is unchanged.

Paths in this patch are prefixed with `linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/`
because conda-build extracts this source with `no_hoist: true` and
applies patches from the recipe's work_dir (one level above the
upstream root).
---
 linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/third_party/CMakeLists.txt | 16 +++++++++++-----
 1 file changed, 11 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)
diff --git a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/third_party/CMakeLists.txt b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/third_party/CMakeLists.txt
index 0f7c3ad..f20f217 100644
--- a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/third_party/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/third_party/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -14,9 +14,15 @@ if (ENABLE_NPU_PERFETTO_BUILD)
   include(cmake/perfetto.cmake)
 endif()
 
-set(INSTALL_GTEST OFF)
-add_subdirectory(googletest EXCLUDE_FROM_ALL)
+# googletest and yaml-cpp are only consumed by the validation test apps
+# (validation/umd-test/, gated by ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD). Skip
+# add_subdirectory() on them when validation is off so that downstream
+# packagers can omit those vendored sources entirely. For yaml-cpp we
+# also prefer a system / conda-forge package via find_package() in the
+# validation branch.
+if (ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD)
+    set(INSTALL_GTEST OFF)
+    add_subdirectory(googletest EXCLUDE_FROM_ALL)
 
-set(YAML_CPP_INSTALL OFF)
-set(BUILD_SHARED_LIBS OFF)
-add_subdirectory(yaml-cpp EXCLUDE_FROM_ALL)
+    find_package(yaml-cpp CONFIG REQUIRED)
+endif()
